data.description: Enjoy this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 car attached garage townhome located in "The Shores" great location! Covered patio, backing to the pond, waterfall and fountains! Walking trails within the community.  Recently renovated with new flooring and white kitchen cabinets, beautiful backsplash. This home features a unique floor plan with spacious owners' suite, double closets, living room with 12Ft ceiling and a cozy wood burning fireplace. The family room also has a wood burning fireplaces to enjoy on the cool evenings. The basement has plenty of storage and a nonconforming bedroom. You will enjoy the indoor/outdoor pool all year round. Easy access to the highways! Bring offer!
